# Cloudflare deploy

## Runtime

- **Workers** + `@opennextjs/cloudflare` (see `docs/adr/001-workers-opennext.md`).
- Worker entry: `.open-next/worker.js` (`wrangler.jsonc`).

## Local verification

| Command | Use |
|---------|-----|
| `pnpm dev` | Fast UI iteration (Next.js only) |
| `pnpm preview` | OpenNext + workerd — **production-like** |
| `pnpm build` | Produce `.open-next/` (Next + OpenNext bundle) |
| `pnpm deploy` | `pnpm build` + `opennextjs-cloudflare deploy` |

Prefer `pnpm preview` before assuming edge/middleware behavior matches production.

## CI / deploy

- **Production:** Cloudflare Workers Builds — build `pnpm run build`, deploy `npx wrangler deploy`.
- **GitHub Actions:** quality only (`lint`, `typecheck`, `test`, `pnpm build`); no GHA deploy job.
- Do not set Workers Builds deploy to `pnpm run deploy` when build already runs `pnpm build`.

## Post-deploy checks

Use Cloudflare observability MCP for 5xx on:

- `/invite/match/*`, `/invite/group/*`
- `/auth/callback`

See README Cloudflare MCP checklist.
